            ++ 3.1.1.1 Results and Discussion ..................... 4
* 4 Conclusion ...................................................... 5
    * 4.1 Summary ................................................... 5
    * 4.2 Future Work ............................................... 5

Note that the TOC entries will include the section numbers, titles, and page numbers (if you're using a class that supports page numbers, such as `report` or `book`). You can customize the appearance of the TOC using various options and packages available in LaTeX.

